rooms.roomDescription: Main floor full bath with walkout to backyard.
Walk in pantry, extra high two car garage with storage/work bench. Outside entrance as well.
Formal dining room with large windows - lots of sun.
Open floor plan family room with custom build ins.
Large chef kitchen with extra dessert bar, mini fridge, propane 6 burner stove with walk in pantry. many upgrades - see attached sheet.
Full guest bathroom with extra deep soaking tub and heat lamps.
Primary bedroom suite with walk in closet (California closet kit), bright windows, fan, carpet, tray ceiling and extra large primary bathroom suite.
Laundry area in basement along with deep sink. Extra refrigerator and supplemental breaker panel for additional electric in the backyard. Separate entrance.

Sitting room/Living Room with custom built fireplace with reclaimed wooden mantle and bluestone. Custom shiplap wall. 5 inch solid wood floors throughout. Plenty of windows and sun. Pocket doors to enter the family room/kitchen.
Three guest bathrooms with fans, carpet, large bright windows and large closets.
Primary bathroom suite with extra large soaking tub, custom shutters, huge shower with dual shower features and double sinks. (See attached notes)

data.description: Stunning 4 bedroom Post Modern  in a desired community on a non-buildable preserve. Located at the end of the cul-de-sac, this house (one of the largest) is a custom build with no detail forgotten. The house opens to a grand 2 story entrance. XL windows, custom shutters and lights create a warming grand atmosphere. 1st floor open floor plan consists of custom gourmet kitchen with under cabinet lighting, mini fridge and walk in pantry. A living space with custom built-ins and pocket doors open to the sitting room with a shiplap wall, wood burning fireplace of bluestone and reclaimed wood.  Dining room with grand windows, and a full bath with entrance to the backyard. The 2nd floor consists of 3 guest bedrooms with large windows/closets. The guest bath has warming lights and an extra deep soaking tub. The primary suite has a tray ceiling, walk-in closet (California) and exquisite primary bath; dual shower features, an XL soaking tub and custom shutters/double sinks. Minutes from all!
